data.description: PRICED TO SELL NOW! NO DOWN PAYMENT, FHA financing available! Buy now before the market gets overly competitive again! If you’re looking for a two-story END UNIT in one of the most highly sought after communities in Aliso Viejo and some of the best schools in Southern California,then this is the home for you!The inviting appeal of the residence starts with the fenced in front yard w/ artificial grass,perfect for kids&pets to play in or just take in the afternoon sun.Offering 3 spacious bedrooms&1.5 baths,including a downstairs 1/2 bath,this home offers much needed space for first time home buyers,a small family or empty nesters.Entering the home,you are greeted by a nicely sized family & dining room w/laminate floors,a cozy gas fireplace,a well-appointed kitchen,&great natural light.The quaint kitchen has granite counters w/ white cabinetry&matte black pulls&handles,stainless steel appliances & a laundry closet w/a stacked washer/dryer & pantry space w/ shelving.Off the family room sliding doors lead to a private & nicely sized back patio w/a deck,perfect for enjoying family & friends,a nice evening BBQ,or a morning cup of coffee.Back inside,the open floor plan continues upstairs where there are 3 beds & a full hallway bath w/a shower/tub.The owner’s suite offers vaulted ceilings w/a ceiling fan,carpet flooring,a large closet & sliders to a balcony,perfect for enjoying private outdoor time.The nicely sized secondary bedrooms have carpet flooring,large closets & share a full hallway bath.Other highlights include scraped ceilings throughout,laminate floors downstairs,stackable washer/dryer,newer AC,Nest thermostat, keyless door entry,new screen & back closet doors,refinished bathtub,new door handles,garbage disposal & kitchen faucet.Enjoy one assigned detached carport w/ storage close to the unit & plenty of street parking.The Morningside Terrace tract offers a pool,spa, barbeque area, & ample green belt space to enjoy the outdoors.Close to exceptional schools,including Wood Canyon elementary school & Saddleback College,a short bike ride to several community parks including Aliso Viejo Community park that offers baseball & soccer fields,green space w/ picnic & playground areas,& the fine dining,entertainment & shops at Aliso Viejo Town Center Mall!Also nearby are Costco,Whole Foods,Aliso Viejo Dog Park,Library & Senior Center, Laguna Niguel Lake Trails & Aliso Viejo Country Club.Easy access to 405/5freeways & 73/133 Toll roads & just minutes to PCH!
